# Angular UI (`ui/`)

## Stack

Angular 21 standalone components, signals, PrimeNG 21, Tailwind 4. API base: `environment.runnerApiUrl` (default `http://localhost:5050`).

## Key surfaces

- `start-run-form` — plan picker, parameter groups, **Show hidden fields** toggle
- `plans-panel` / `plans-page` — upload, download, delete plans
- `run-detail-page` — logs, samples, HTML report
- `runner.service.ts` — all API calls

## Hidden fields

`isUiHiddenParam()`: hide when `param.hidden` (JMX `HIDE`) **or** `kind === 'header'`. Toggle reveals them with a badge. Empty groups are omitted.

## API dropdowns

Load via `POST /field-options` with current `planFile` + form `props`. Re-resolve when parent `depends` fields change. Load options for hidden API fields too so the toggle works.

## Labels

Use `param.label` from JMX `LABEL=` when present; else format `param.name` via `format-field-label`.

## Style

Match existing SCSS/Tailwind patterns in sibling components. Avoid drive-by refactors outside the requested UI area.
